  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK369">
<l>iṉpa miṭaiyaṟā tīṇṭu mavāveṉṉun</l>
<l>tuṉpattuṭ ṭuṉpaṅ keṭiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even while in this body, joy will never depart (from the mind, in which) desire, that sorrow of sorrows, has been destroyed.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
